# Firebase google-services.json (real credentials per flavor — NEVER commit)
# Real creds live in flavor source sets so the Firebase gradle plugin
# auto-picks the right file per build variant. The .example placeholders
# are committed so contributors know the expected file shape.
/app/src/dev/google-services.json
/app/src/prod/google-services.json
/app/google-services.json
!/app/src/dev/google-services.json.example
!/app/src/prod/google-services.json.example